Titolo: Elsinore (video game)

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Elsinore is a 2019 point-and-click adventure game developed and published by Golden Glitch for Windows, Linux, and MacOS. The game follows the character of Ophelia from William Shakespeare's Hamlet. In Elsinore, Ophelia has a vision of the deaths of everyone in Elsinore Castle and relives the same four days again and again as she works to prevent the tragedy that will fall over everyone.
Development on Elsinore took over seven years, and was created on nights and weekends by its development team. The game received generally positive reviews from critics, who noted that fans of Hamlet would appreciate it but that the game's slow pace could be sometimes frustrating.